## @ac/common — NestJS Shared Logic

**Phụ thuộc:** `@ac/i18n`, `@ac/utils`, TypeORM, ioredis, lodash, class-validator, axios

**Dùng cho:** decorators, guards, interceptors, pipes, base services, base DTOs.

```ts
// apps/api-typeorm/src/some.service.ts
import { BaseService } from '@ac/common'
import { SomeEntity } from '@ac/models-typeorm'
```

---

## @ac/models-typeorm — TypeORM Entities

```ts
// Trong api-typeorm
import { GiaoDichCongChungEntity } from '@ac/models-typeorm'

// Định nghĩa entity trong package
@Entity('giao_dich_cong_chung')
export class GiaoDichCongChungEntity {
  @PrimaryGeneratedColumn('uuid')
  id: string

  @Column()
  soHopDong: string

  @CreateDateColumn()
  createdAt: Date
}
```

---

## @ac/utils — Pure Utility Functions

Chứa các hàm thuần (không có framework dependency):

```ts
// packages/utils/src/index.ts
export function formatDate(date: Date | string, format = 'dd/MM/yyyy'): string { ... }
export function slugify(text: string): string { ... }
export function chunk<T>(arr: T[], size: number): T[][] { ... }
export function omit<T, K extends keyof T>(obj: T, keys: K[]): Omit<T, K> { ... }
```

